{"tid":1285656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵月台激戰 「劉馬車」與男乘客同被捕 撐警網絡紅人「劉馬車」","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T18:43:01.000Z","uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d41a04d39a6cacfafb9793178374bb61e50f5198","tid":1285656,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SAMyvHe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSAMyvHe.jpg&h=437a32c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n撐警網絡紅人「劉馬車」，傍晚6時許乘搭港鐵時，聲稱遭人用手機拍攝挑釁，雙方初則口角繼而動武，兩人其後於荔枝角站落車，繼續在月台大打出手，雙方的衣服被扯爛，車站職員趕至阻止，將他們分開。警員接報到場，兩人均報稱受傷，須由救護車送院治理。警方經初步調查，以涉嫌公眾地方打架拘捕兩人。 <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190704/59789528?fbclid=IwAR2eHSQfI48RgfIm0vWxH5f9F_H69oystkrU9GckWYt66UZOB3UCQpSm8-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190704%2F59789528%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2eHSQfI48RgfIm0vWxH5f9F_H69oystkrU9GckWYt66UZOB3UCQpSm8-0&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRQ6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=03189bb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190704%2F59789528%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2eHSQfI48RgfIm0vWxH5f9F_H69oystkrU9GckWYt66UZOB3UCQpSm8-0&h=a884d95a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190704/59789528?fbclid=IwAR2eHSQfI48RgfIm0vWxH5f9F_H69oystkrU9GckWYt66UZOB3UCQpSm8-0</a>"},{"pid":"97c7811fc98100ebece32a371ae4cc1b5ccb9df8","tid":1285656,"uid":271561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:43:01.000Z","msg":"劉馬車 的愛國心聲，幫佢話俾13億同胞知道。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=738926539532967&amp;id=369508809808077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D738926539532967%26id%3D369508809808077&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRQ6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=c7949bfd\" target